items.headline: Bella and the Bullfrogs Wiki!
items.desc: The wiki all about the upcoming Nickelodeon comedy series! It's about Bella, a perky cheerleader whose life gets an unexplained twist when she becomes the quarterback for her school team, the Bullfrogs. Bella is then joined by Troy, Newt, her best friend Sophie, Sawyer and Pepper, and their adventures are truly priceless! It stars The Haunted Hathaway's Brec Bassinger, Are We There Yet's Coy Stewart, Wendell and Vinnie's Buddy Handleson and so much more! The wiki is still under construction, but with your help, we can make it a collaborative resource for the upcoming Nick series!
